## Adjacent Artifacts

Supporting files that live alongside the tiers:

| Location              | Purpose                                                                                                                                                                |
| --------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `.prism/templates/`  | Canonical templates (bug report, PR description, acceptance criteria, ticket types). Skills reference, never duplicate.                                                |
| `.prism/references/` | Shared operational flows — plan lookup, architect-context loading, shipping flow. Used by multiple skills.                                                             |
| `.prism/spec/adrs/`  | Architectural Decision Records for durable, cross-cutting decisions — skill ecosystem, codebase architecture, spec structure. Canonical source for decision rationale. |
| `.prism/lessons.md`  | Per-session corrections and discoveries. Lessons promote to rules/architect when they fire more than once.                                                             |

